text: El Afweyn, also known as Ceel Afweyn, is a city in the western Sanaag region of Somaliland. ==Demographics== The city El Afweyn has a total population of 17,574 residents.https://docs.unocha.org/sites/dms/Somalia/UNDP-POP-RURAL- URBAN%202005.pdf ==References== ==External links== *Ceel Afweyn, Somalia Page Category:Populated places in Sanaag
